<h2>Changes</h2>
<ul>
<li>Added an option to individually hide the new Today's News sidebar section on desktop</li>
<li>Fixed individually hiding the broadcasts sidebar section in Home desktop</li>
<li>Fixed hiding Community rules when hiding all sidebar contents on desktop</li>
<li>Fixed waiting for the sidebar in more full-width pages on desktop</li>
<li>Fixed applying translation for Creator Studio option</li>
<li>Fixed option label after new Connect nav item was renamed to Follow</li>
<li>Fixed hiding the new Follow nav item on mobile</li>
<li>Fixed trying to redirect /tos and /privacy URLs, which don't exist on twitter.com</li>
<li>Fixed preserving query parameters when redirecting to twitter.com</li>
<li>Fixed hiding the extra "From domain" link when restoring link headlines, after a Twitter markup change</li>
</ul>
